==English==

===Noun===
'''valetudinarian'''
# a person of a [[weak]] or [[sickly]] [[constitution]]; especially one whose chief concern is being or becoming a [[chronic]] [[invalid]]

====Translations====
*French: [[valétudinaire]]

===Adjective===
'''valetudinarian'''
# constantly [[ill]] or [[concerned]] with one's [[health]]

====Translations====
*French: [[valétudinaire]], [[cacochyme]], [[hypochondriaque]]

====Synonyms====
* [[hypochondriac]]

